items.title: Crew improves standing with shutout of Bucs
items.summary: Ryan Braun homered and five pitchers combined for the Brewers' 11th shutout victory, a 3-0 triumph over the slumping Pirates at PNC Park. With 12 games left on their schedule, the Brewers pulled within 3 1/2 games of the Cubs in the National League Central and two games of the Rockies in the race for the second NL Wild Card.

items.title: Renfroe, Jankowski among 5 Padres callups
items.summary: The Padres added some depth across the board Monday, with Hunter Renfroe headlining a list of five callups to the big league roster.
